Description.Text: A very good standard hotel which offers great value for money. 12/08 SC
The hotel is located in the VDNH area, just off a busy road leading to Moscow's centre. There is a shopping mall and supermarket open 24 hours a day only minutes from the hotel.

The rooms are small to medium-sized and are in very good condition. They are basic but comfortably furnished with dark wooden furniture. Due to good soundproofing, rooms facing the street are not affected by noise from passing traffic.
A modern high-rise building set in a private and guarded area just off the main road.
The restaurant on the ground floor is open for breakfast, lunch and dinner.
The lobby is medium-sized and very welcoming. There is a cosy seating area and lobby bar, along with an internet corner
